{"tid":1272510,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"為保護前線發夢手足，請各位用人潮策略！","createTime":"2019-07-01T11:21:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-01T12:04:59.000Z","uid":99207,"like":75,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"bf00d6333e291e450870034fefb8d86eb1095d08","tid":1272510,"uid":99207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T11:21:35.000Z","msg":"前線嘅手足喺個夢度好努力咁打緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果人一少嘅話啲狗就會衝出嚟清場/包圍<br />\n為咗保護好佢地，為佢地提供人潮防護<br />\n啲狗根本包唔到<br />\n而且同時係俾路佢地做返個和理非<br />\n所以！就算你衝唔衝、就算你係溫和派都好<br />\n只要你棟個人喺度，佔領住條路，你已經有好大嘅貢獻同幫助<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n求下你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔好散啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地班後生仔會保護你地<br />\n而溫和嘅你地都可以保護我地架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nP.S. 打完篇文我又去搵周公lu<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bfdede86a05d4c10070568e2b8414fdeeebbc1b","tid":1272510,"uid":99207,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T11:22:11.000Z","msg":"推啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔可以再有人犧牲架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9bb6ff699e75e948b8494f88b6d839d181d79ac","tid":1272510,"uid":34515,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T11:22:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">轉：立會需要水、頭盔、索帶、遮、first aid、較剪、眼罩、盾牌、紙皮、六角匙、頭盔、較剪<br />\n物資短缺！<br />\n拎去煲底</span></span>"},{"pid":"39a73f2be70976994f970296fc238c0a0cb7d86e","tid":1272510,"uid":99207,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T11:22:34.000Z","msg":"幫手推上熱門俾仲行緊嘅人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gi